{"tid":540241,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【回帶】每人一條以前好笑嘅YouTube片","createTime":"2018-01-25T09:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-25T13:13:39.000Z","uid":34394,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e2a1b58b0a16894e88de04680836126a23e488","tid":540241,"uid":34394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"而家YouTube<br />\n充斥住一班傻閪經營嘅小學雞頻道<br />\n同埋內容農場<br />\n但係<br />\n曾經佢帶俾我哋好多嘅歡樂<br />\n一條又一條唔知乜鳩又好好笑嘅片<br />\n永遠留喺我哋嘅記憶之中<br />\n<br />\n德國小孩打爆keyboard<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M8pR1rZZHEs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM8pR1rZZHEs&d=eV%2BAlnDYlvQ81GvqFlsP%2BP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8ffbeeb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M8pR1rZZHEs</a><br />\n<br />\n魔獸世界帳號俾老母刪除<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YersIyzsOpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYersIyzsOpc&d=eV%2BAlnDYlvQ81GvqFlsP%2BP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e260d6a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YersIyzsOpc</a><br />\n<br />\n賣而啊嘻<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KmtzQCSh6xk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKmtzQCSh6xk&d=eV%2BAlnDYlvQ81GvqFlsP%2BP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=bfeb6a70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KmtzQCSh6xk</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然冇高清甚至4K嘅畫面<br />\n仲未賣俾Google<br />\n但係個陣時候<br />\nYouTube係最精彩嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93a79be16fbf60f7b9bafa55757951be2e7f5ccb","tid":540241,"uid":27939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"某校勁band<br />\n海底奇兵"},{"pid":"e19ec5d2a5d74527af417b48b10f690c09af5479","tid":540241,"uid":26106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T09:57:19.000Z","msg":"其實呢三